{"tid":92943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【他朝君體也相同】灣仔站炒扶手梯 目擊者：好似撞車聲","createTime":"2017-01-24T04:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T11:46:48.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9fd8140fb682330d58065e866646286de70818","tid":92943,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"【11:37 更新】港鐵發言人回應。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵灣仔站今晨繁忙時間有「炒扶手梯」事故。讀者畢先生今早9時35分，乘港鐵抵達灣仔站，繼而登乘扶手梯上大堂，突然聽到「呯」一聲「好似撞車聲」響，隨即有市民驚叫。他循聲查看，原來旁邊另一條上行扶手梯最頂一級「蹺起咗，有個窿」。「當時有乘客啱啱去到嗰個位，好彩跳起跨過咗」沒有受傷，尾隨其後人亦紛紛跨步而過，港鐵職員其後將扶手梯封鎖。畢先生說，上班繁忙時間非常多人，慶幸今次沒有任何人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，上午9時35分左右，車站控制室亮起燈號，顯示連接1號月台及車站大堂的一條扶手梯停止運作，職員趕往了解，發現扶手梯上端有損壞，於是將扶手梯圍住，並通知承辦商到場檢查。<br />\n<br />\n發言人提醒，乘客使用扶手梯時多加留意，不要站近梯邊，避免有衣物或鞋履攝入扶手梯邊，並「企定定」免生意外。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170124&amp;guid=56215101&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170124%26guid%3D56215101%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Y5poOtfUGlYmbpleFHkHqmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=1021828b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170124%26guid%3D56215101%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=1c694036\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170124&amp;guid=56215101&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"28ff1d0f5852b3ae9540ca1a1d38e1ddba0a5f6b","tid":92943,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f1081370f96fea23edbc8426d4d3794de10c28","tid":92943,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"與祖國接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690c4526203e86c884d47935cb74394506edbf66","tid":92943,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"咩牌子？"},{"pid":"96e83603a80710594f6f1c3cb52a120a86eb629c","tid":92943,"uid":18698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:40:42.000Z","msg":"合符國情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d99d90637bbb1dc5a9be0bbeb9bcf795ec0a15","tid":92943,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩牌子？</blockquote><br />\n依好多用大陸野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368a3352137058065b0d7abf6b91a0e11827a371","tid":92943,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"買就日本原廠<br />\n零件貪平轉用次貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec613d78023725b372f0eb778daf6d0e7991c15","tid":92943,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思又加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc62198252e10b384ef50e647208be0e817d905","tid":92943,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"乘客問題"},{"pid":"33e0f8dc361585898654144a9ff995bac0946378","tid":92943,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"扶手梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm